<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99606958249212></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99606958249212><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=3&mid=99606958249212>RE: Items</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Jul 25th 9:59 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>well you don't say how much "lots" of pp is but heres the basics:<br><br>   Try to get at least a full set of Cured Silk or Wu's besides the pieces that I will name.<br><br>   For weapons try to get either two Fighting Batons or a Fighting Baton and Essence of Dol. Two good combos there.<br><br>   For your head try to get an Executioners Hood. For your Chest try to get a Crystal Covered Shroud or a Lockjaw Hide vest (CCS being much better then LH vest). For your face try to get a Sarnak Hide Mask. For your gloves get Gem Inaid Gauntlets, great until your 40's. For your Shoulders get a Drolvarg Mantle, great till your 50's. For rings try to get either Golden Fire Wedding Rings (4AC 45HP) or Platinum fire Wedding Rings (6AC 65HP). For earrings try to get either Cougar Claw or Orc Fang, both are good but Cougar Claw is better. <br><br>  Well I hope this helped.<br><br>Graylance Moonfist<br>Lvl 22 Monk<br>Vazelle Server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
