	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hi, I am a lvl 21 Monk. I am currently in South Karana hunting the Aviaks, but the problem I have there is that there is no bank anywhere near it. So... is there anywhere else that I could hunt that I wouldn't have to run across the whole continent to get to the bank? Thanks. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
