	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you want good plat, all I have to say is Ocean of Tears.  Hunt on the haunted island (neg1000, neg6000 aprox) and kill gargoyles.  They drop stackable eyes which are worth 7-8pp to merchants.  They should also be good exp at your level, and if you're an iksar, they give positive bard faction.  Traveling to and from the zone is my only problem.  IMO, the easiest way to leave OOT and get back to Freeport is by finding a small boat (they can be found on several island, and you can drive them by right clicking on them while you're standing on it, you can stop driving it by right clicking it again) and taking it to the loc (neg4643, &lt;second number doesnt matter for this&gt;) then right click on the boat to regain control of yourself, face west, and when you see the boat jump in the water and swim through the hull.  Great exp and great loot.<br>&nbsp;<br>Burrusu<br>30 Iksar Monk<br>"Wu's pants are neon green?  Trance stick?  He must be a stripper"</td></tr>
