<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99568609617259></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99568609617259><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=3&mid=99568609617259>What's the Damage on your fists per lvl</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
